What did you say?

35
00:03:47,378 --> 00:03:48,579
A settlement?

36
00:03:48,748 --> 00:03:50,188
Why should I?

37
00:03:50,188 --> 00:03:52,019
I'm just trying to help you.

38
00:03:52,389 --> 00:03:55,319
The assailants are from wealthy families.

39
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:57,859
So you're telling me to accept Tae Ju's wrongful death?

40
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:00,829
Since they're from wealthy families?

41
00:04:01,458 --> 00:04:03,229
Since I won't win the trial?

42
00:04:03,468 --> 00:04:05,599
I heard you passed the bar exam.

43
00:04:06,568 --> 00:04:10,109
You'll soon be working in this field as well.

44
00:04:10,109 --> 00:04:12,539
No. I will never do that.

45
00:04:13,578 --> 00:04:15,678
So relay my message to the scumbags.

46
00:04:17,649 --> 00:04:18,649
Tell them to come here immediately,

47
00:04:18,649 --> 00:04:20,678
kneel, and ask my brother for forgiveness.

48
00:04:22,318 --> 00:04:23,719
If not,

49
00:04:25,549 --> 00:04:26,589
tell them I'll kill them.

50
00:04:31,388 --> 00:04:34,959
This DUI case occurred on November 21, 2012,

51
00:04:35,359 --> 00:04:36,768
at 5:30am,

52
00:04:36,768 --> 00:04:41,198
at Mullae-dong, Yeongdeungpo-gu.

53
00:04:41,438 --> 00:04:44,839
Lee Tae Ju, a delivery man, died in the accident.

54
00:04:45,438 --> 00:04:48,438
Defendants Kang Ho Young, Koo Dae Hwan,

55
00:04:48,438 --> 00:04:50,149
