56
00:04:51,008 --> 00:04:52,808
According to Article 3, Clause 1...

57
00:04:52,808 --> 00:04:54,049
of Act on Special Cases concerning the Settlement of Traffic Accidents,

58
00:04:55,049 --> 00:04:56,049
I declare them innocent.

59
00:04:56,448 --> 00:04:58,818
According to Article 268 of the Criminal Code,

60
00:04:58,818 --> 00:04:59,849
I declare them innocent.

61
00:05:00,049 --> 00:05:03,888
According to Article 44, Clause 1 of the Road Traffic Act,

62
00:05:03,888 --> 00:05:05,258
I acknowledge a part of the crime.

63
00:05:05,428 --> 00:05:09,998
Defendants Kang Ho Young, Koo Dae Hwan, and Jo Yeon Woo...

64
00:05:09,998 --> 00:05:11,229
will be sentenced to eight months in prison,

65
00:05:11,229 --> 00:05:13,498
and a year and six months of probation.

66
00:05:13,638 --> 00:05:15,498
They'll be fined 6,000 dollars,

67
00:05:15,498 --> 00:05:18,438
and they'll perform community service for 81 days.

68
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,448
Shouldn't they pay...

69
00:05:32,388 --> 00:05:34,359
according to what's right?

70
00:05:35,419 --> 00:05:37,558
An innocent boy died, yet you declared this...

71
00:05:37,558 --> 00:05:38,558
an accidental homicide?

72
00:05:38,828 --> 00:05:40,258
81 days of community service?

73
00:05:40,859 --> 00:05:43,428
How was this accidental? How?

74
00:05:45,229 --> 00:05:46,268
Are you smiling?

75
00:05:46,938 --> 00:05:47,969
What's wrong with him?

76
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:51,669
- Bring my brother back! - You shouldn't do this.

77
00:05:52,268 --> 00:05:54,479
You. I'll kill you all.

78
00:05:54,479 --> 00:05:55,709
You can't do this.

79
00:05:55,709 --> 00:05:57,349
How is this the law?

80
00:05:57,349 --> 00:05:59,349
Let me go! Let me go!

81
00:05:59,849 --> 00:06:00,948
Let me go!

82
00:06:02,018 --> 00:06:04,318
Come here. Come here!

83
00:06:04,618 --> 00:06:06,089
Come here right now!

84
00:06:07,518 --> 00:06:08,818
You scumbags.

